GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE BILL 166
Short Title: Repeal Limitations On Auxiliary Containers. (Public)
Sponsors: Senators Mayfield, Murdock, and Chitlik (Primary Sponsors).
Referred to: Rules and Operations of the Senate
February 26, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO REPEAL LIMITATIONS ON AUXILIARY CONTAINERS.
3 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
4 SECTION 1. G.S. 153A-145.12 and G.S. 160A-205.7 are repealed.
5 SECTION 2. This act is effective when it becomes law.
